------------------------------------------------------------------------------
                                 Introduction
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Raster Master is an Amos copper generator, for editing colour tables
and copper bars (how useful in this day and age!).

It's based on Rainbow Warrior, by Martyn Brown(spadge) - a program that's
now 9 years old!

